title: E411 Tony Hinchcliffe

description:
Tony Hinchcliffe joins the show for the first time. He and Theo talk about how they both got into stand-up, the debate between Austin and LA, Tony’s crazy childhood in Ohio, and a lot more. 

Tony Hinchcliffe is a stand-up comedian, writer, and host of the live podcast Kill Tony, with new episodes every Monday.
